 ed bangers\, we’re revisiting the sounds that defined 2016 and the cultur
 e that came with it.\nParticipants will go head-to-head\, battling throug
 h categories from our childhood. Think you know the song of the summer? T
 he ultimate party anthem? The track that had everyone in their feelings? 
 This is your moment to prove it.\nWhether you’re here to win\, vibe\, or 
 just relive the memories\, Aux Wars: 2016 Edition is all about good music
 \, good energy\, and a little friendly competition. Who’s taking the aux?
