DESCRIPTION:This isn’t just a “discussion”—this is a safe but real space f
 or men to speak freely about pressure\, identity\, mental health\, and wh
 at it actually means to be a man right now. Think barbershop energy: hone
 st\, unfiltered\, and relatable.\nAttendees can pull up\, get a free hair
 cut\, tap into an open mic conversation\, and walk away with resources an
 d wellness products that actually matter.\nThis event is designed to:\n\n
 Build trust and brotherhood on campus\nNormalize conversations around men
 tal health and masculinity\nGive men a space where they’re heard\, not ju
 dged\n\n\nHosted by: Omega Psi Phi\n\nAdditional Information can be found
  at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12389091
