DESCRIPTION:This event is a fun celebration of creativity\, culture and co
 mmunity bringing students together to honor Earth Day. 🌎\nThroughout the
  afternoon\, participants can engage in a range of hands-on activities su
 ch as sun printing\, painting sessions\, flower pot painting\, and dreamc
 atcher making. There will also be a special performance by the LASO Dance
  Troupe\, highlighting the student talent on campus.\nDesigned to inspire
  creativity and appreciation for nature\, the event offers a welcoming sp
