DESCRIPTION:On behalf of EngageNJ\, we are excited to announce our 7th Ann
 ual THRIVE Conference will be hosted at Montclair State University\, 7th 
 Floor Conference Center on April 21st from 9:00AM - 3:00 PM!\n \nConferen
 ce Highlights: \nThis conference is FREE to all attendees! \nGain insight
 s from professionals and student leaders who are paving the way for the f
 uture generation.\nBreakfast & lunch are provided. \n \nClick here to reg
 ister  https://forms.monday.com/forms/adb42295b54232821c8d33cbc5ffee16?r=
 use1 \n \nThe deadline to register for this conference is Monday\, April 
 6th.\n \nWe are looking for presenters! We are seeking workshops centered
  around professional development\, student leadership\, or community buil
 ding. The workshop should be 45 minutes in total. The deadline to submit 
 this form is March 31st.\n \nIf you have any questions\, please feel free
  to reach out to perezso@montclair.edu or info@engagenj.org\n\nHosted by:
  Office of Community Engagement and Partnerships\n\nAdditional Informatio
 n can be found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12372564
