 ainting materials will be provided\, and participants are encouraged to c
 reate artwork that reflects their personal inspiration. No prior artistic
  experience is required—everyone is welcome to participate.\nWe look forw
 ard to an enjoyable and engaging gathering that promotes community\, crea
 tivity\, and relaxation. ✨\nLocation: (Bloomfield Campus) Franklin Hall -
  Fourth Floor Rooftop (414)\n\nHosted by: Bloomfield's Office of Residenc
 e Life\n\nAdditional Information can be found at: https://montclair.campu
 slabs.com/engage/event/12401680
