DESCRIPTION:Participate in Campus Earth Month throughout April by collecti
 ng code words and earning entries to win prizes. Each code word you colle
 ct or action you complete will earn an entry into the Campus Earth Month 
 Raffle. The more entries you earn\, the better your odds.\nEach decision 
 you make has the potential to be good for the planet and people. No one c
 an do it all\, but we can all do something. This April\, make sure your l
 edger is balanced so you are always…+1 for the Planet\, People\, Yourself
 \, & Montclair!\nYour goal is to collect as many code words as you can th
 roughout April. At every in-person Earth Month event\, a code word will b
 e available. It will either be displayed at the event or communicated to 
 you during the event verbally. When the event concludes\, you can also as
 k the organizer for the code word.\nSustainability Student Interns will b
 e out on campus with opportunities to earn additional code words and code
  words will also be available virtually.\nYou are responsible for keeping
  track of your code words while participating and submitting them all in 
 one email to sustainability@montclair.edu by April\, 30 2026.\nEach decis
 ion you make has the potential to be good for the planet. No one can do i
 t all\, but we can all do something. This April\, make sure your ledger i
 s balanced so you are always…+1 for the Planet\, People\, Yourself\, & Mo
 ntclair! ❤️🌎😊🦅🐻Full details\, including additional Raffle entry optio
 ns\, a complete prize list\, & rules are available at: https://www.montcl
 air.edu/sustainability/earth-month/For a full-list of events visit here: 
 https://www.montclair.edu/sustainability/earth-month-events/\n\nHosted by
 : Office of Sustainability\n\nOnline Location: https://www.instagram.com/
 p/DWlvj7tEYTQ/?img_index=1\n\nAdditional Information can be found at: htt
 ps://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12390150
DTEND:20260430T210000Z
DTSTAMP:20260407T030159Z
DTSTART:20260401T120000Z
LOCATION:Montclair + Bloomfield Campuses
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Campus Earth Month
